name: Chewbacca Of Kashyyyk (V)
Lore: 'Wookiee scout. Volunteered for Han''s Endor strike team. Keeps his distance, but doesn''t look like he''s keeping his distance. Always thinks with his stomach.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots.  Deploys -2 to Kashyyyk.  Wookiees are destiny +1 when drawn for weapon or battle destiny.  While stacked on Grrrghrrrgh!, Wookiees are power and forfeit +1.  While hit, Chewie''s power is doubled.(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
